                            <comment id="12657275" author="bmargulies" created="Wed, 17 Dec 2008 03:37:13 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It would be really helpful if you could add in a test case that we can check in, as I don&apos;t have a way to regress this as things are. If you can&apos;t, I&apos;ll look for help from the people doing OSGI around CXF.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
